        "subheading": "",
        "title": "Exfoliate",
        "content": "<p>Exfoliating once or twice a week can help to remove dead skin cells and improve the appearance of dry skin. Use a gentle exfoliator that is designed for dry skin, such as enzymatic exfoliators, AHAs, and PHAs.<\/p>",
